b'Ichigo Mashimaro':
b'"Cute girls doing cute things in cute ways."

Everyday things make up the fabric of life\xe2\x80\x94whether it's making friends, going to school, trying to make money, or celebrating a holiday. Ichigo Mashimaro is a heartwarming series that follows the daily lives of Itou Chika, her sister Nobue, and her friends Miu, Matsuri, and Ana.
